            <!-- BEGIN: Cognitive-Services-TopBanner -->
            <div class="common-banner col-top-banner" data-config="{'backgroundColor':'#e3f4ff', 'backgroundImage':'//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/cognitive-face-api-slice-01.png','imageHeight':'auto'}">
                <div class="common-banner-image">
                    <div class="common-banner-title">
                        <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,face.png" />
                        <h2>>Face API<span>Face API</span></h2>
                        <h4>Detects relatively similar faces based on similar images grouped together, recognizing previously marked persons in the images.</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="face_1rmb-trial">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="face_pia">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- END: Cognitive-Services-TopBanner --> <!-- BEGIN: Cognitive-Services-Content -->
            <div class="pricing-page-section">   
                <h2>Face Verification</h2> 
                <p>Examines two faces and can determine if they are the same person. The API returns a confidence rating, describes how confident it is that it is the same person.</p>
                <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/cognitive-services/cognitive-services-face-c01.png" class="cognitive-banner"/>                                                                
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">   
                <h2>Face Detection</h2> 
                <p>Detects if an image contains a face or faces and locates the face in a rectangle against the background and includes machine learning to predict the characteristics of a face. Facial attributes recognized include: age, expression, gender, posture, smile, and facial hair. It can detect 27 facial attributes in an image.</p>
                <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/cognitive-services/cognitive-services-face-people.png" class="cognitive-banner"/>                                                                
            </div>
            
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <!-- <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/cognitive-services/cognitive-services-face-verification.png"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>人脸验证</h2>
                        <p>核对两张脸是否属于同一个人。并给出置信度评分。</p>
                    </div>
                </div> -->
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/cognitive-services/cognitive-services-face-identification.png"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Facial Recognition</h2>
                        <p>Search for and recognize faces. It uses user-provided data to tag a person or group to conduct a search and to match with a previously seen face.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/cognitive-services/cognitive-services-face-similar-face-search.png"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Similar Face Searches</h2>
                        <p>Easily find similar faces. Given a set of faces and a new face, conduct a search. The API will return if a similar face is in the group.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/cognitive-services/cognitive-services-face-grouping.png"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Face Grouping</h2>
                        <p>According to the degree of visual similarity, it will make a group from faces it cannot recognize.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h1>Learn about the Cognitive Services API</h1>
                <ul class="cognitive-icon-group">
                    <li>
                        <div class="cognitive-icon"><img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,face.png"/></div>
                        <div class="cognitive-text">
                            <h2>Face API</h2>
                            <p>Detects relatively similar faces based on similar images grouped together, recognizing previously marked persons in the images.</p>
                            <p><a id="face_face" href="/home/features/cognitive-services/face/" class="single-link">More<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>                    
                    <li>
                        <div class="cognitive-icon"><img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,emotion.png"/></div>
                        <div class="cognitive-text">
                            <h2>- Emotion API</h1>
                            <p>Analyzes the face to detect emotions and personalizes the application’s response.</p>
                            <p><a id="face_emotion" href="/home/features/cognitive-services/emotion/" class="single-link">More<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="cognitive-icon"><img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,computer-vision.png"/></div>
                        <div class="cognitive-text">
                           <h2>Computer Vision API</h2>
                        <p>Extract enrichment data from images to categorize and handle visual data, inspect images with computer assistance, provide help for curation services.</p>
                        <p><a id="face_computer-vision" href="/home/features/cognitive-services/computer-vision/" class="single-link">More<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                    
