    <metaDescription><![CDATA[The Azure Cognitive Services Face API can detect one or more faces in an image. It can also mark a face with a border while making a facial attribute prediction using machine learning. After a person’s face is detected, you can use the face frame directly as an input to the Emotion API to rapidly process the image. Facial features recognized include age, gender, attitude, smile and facial hair, along with 27 important facial characteristics.]]></metaDescription>
